description:
Work to trees in TPO 005
 T67 and  T70 Cedar - tip reduce, removing no more than 0.5m; T94 Yew - cut to clear windows/building by 1.5m; 
 T65 Catalpa (Tree of Heaven) - fell;  
 
 Work to various unprotected trees
 T1 Sycamore - reduce crown by no more than 3m
 G1 Sycamore x 3 - crown lift to 3m
 T24 Prunus - fell
